This design system distills the look and feel of the Cashflow product. Per the
project README, the upstream Cashflow repository
(https://github.com/Connor-Adams/cashflow) is **source-available for review only,
not open-source**.

Before publishing this repository with an open-source license (e.g. MIT or
Apache-2.0), confirm with the upstream owner that you have the right to
redistribute these tokens, components, and brand assets. Do NOT assume MIT
applies just because this file is a placeholder.

Once cleared, replace this file with your chosen license text. Common choices:

  - MIT          — simplest, most permissive
  - Apache-2.0   — permissive + explicit patent grant

Until then, treat this repository as: Copyright (c) 2026 — all rights reserved.
